q = int(input())
for _ in range(q):
    n = int(input())
    a = list(map(int, input().split()))
    for i in range(n):
        if a[i] > a[i+1]:
            a[i], a[i+1] = a[i+1], a[i]
            break
    #print(a)
    for i in range(n-1):
        if a[i] > a[i+1]:
            a[i], a[i+1] = a[i+1], a[i]
            break
    print(*a)

from sys import stdin
from itertools import permutations

q = int(stdin.readline())

for _ in range(q):
    n = int(stdin.readline())
    p = list(map(int, stdin.readline().split()))
    p = list(permutations(p))
    p.sort()
    print(*p[0])

from sys import stdin
from itertools import permutations

q = int(stdin.readline())

for _ in range(q):
    n = int(stdin.readline())
    p = list(map(int, stdin.readline().split()))
    p = list(permutations(p, n))
    p.sort()
    print(*p[0])
